  description: Increases Attack Damage by 20% and Magic Resist by 3. Heals the wearer
    for 20% of all damage dealt.Once per combat, when the wearer's Health is about
    to fall below 40%, they instantly generate a Shield equal to 25% of their Maximum
    Health for 5 seconds.. A tattered crimson cloak paired with a jagged blade, both
    cursed with an insatiable hunger for the life essence of others.
